Life is a journey, not a destination. We do not live merely to pass the days,
but to feel, to think, to love, and to grow. Every challenge we face shapes our character,
every failure teaches us wisdom, and every small success gives us courage to move forward.
Do not regret the past, do not worry too much about the future,
but cherish the present moment, for time never comes back once it is gone.
Keep a gentle heart, keep a firm mind, walk steadily on your own path,
and let time witness all your efforts and changes.
